## Operator Breakdown

- **σ (Air/Aerunik — Distinction)**: explanatory|non_explanatory — Explanatory knowledge is portable threads; non-explanatory is inherited knots acting blindly.
- **ρ (Water/Sentaria — Relation)**: thread|knot — Conjecture and criticism as circulation engine of knowledge creation.
- **λ (Fire/Jvalion — Transformation)**: conjecture|criticism — Error transformed from moral failure to fuel. Punishing critique makes knots masquerade as truths.
- **β (Wood/Arboriel — Growth)**: error_correction|innovation_starvation — Fast error cycling accelerates thread mutation, improving selection.
- **δγ (Earth/Humavita — Cycling)**: conservative_knots|exploratory_threads — Cultural evolution initially favors low-variance knots over exploratory threads.
- **μ (Metal/Ferrosid — Structure)**: authority|fallibilism — No infallible authority. Education teaches generation and criticism, not memorization.

## Z-State
